arts.ttl: Rayo Vallecano close in on European spot as winning streak continues
arts.sum: Rayo Vallecano remain on course to clinch European qualification for the first time in over two decades. Inigo Perez’s side sealed a third successive La Liga win as they battled past rock bottom Real Valladolid to move up sixth in the table.
